ZH: 这份书是他争辩的佐证。
EN: This book is proof of his argument.

ZH: 这份文件会作为证据来佐证他的无辜。
EN: This document will serve as evidence to support his innocence.

ZH: 她提供了一些照片作为佐证。
EN: She provided some photos as evidence.

ZH: 这个实验结果佐证了我的猜测。
EN: The result of this experiment confirmed my hypothesis.

ZH: 这段录音是他的话语的佐证。
EN: This recording serves as evidence of his words.

ZH: 这些证据可以佐证他的行为是合法的。
EN: These pieces of evidence can support the legality of his actions.

ZH: 他找到了一位专家作为他论点的佐证。
EN: He found an expert to serve as evidence for his argument.

ZH: 这份报告能够佐证我们的观点是正确的。
EN: This report can provide evidence that our point of view is correct.

ZH: 这份报告为我们的结论提供了有力的佐证。
EN: This report provides strong evidence for our conclusion.

ZH: 这些病人的反馈佐证了治疗方法的有效性。
EN: The feedback from these patients provides evidence of the effectiveness of the treatment method.

ZH: 这个案件的视频资料为警方提供了重要的佐证。
EN: The video footage of this case provides crucial evidence for the police.

ZH: 这位证人的证词为被告提供了有力的佐证。
EN: The testimony of this witness provides strong evidence for the defendant.

ZH: 这份文件的内容可以佐证他的身份。
EN: The content of this document can serve as evidence of his identity.

ZH: 他的日记记录佐证了他的旅行经历。
EN: His diary entries provide evidence of his travel experience.

ZH: 这些数据为我们的研究结果提供了佐证。
EN: These data provide evidence for our research findings.

ZH: 这个实例可以作为佐证，说明我们的理论是正确的。
EN: This example can serve as proof that our theory is correct.

ZH: 这段录像是对他们不当行为的直接佐证。
EN: This video footage is direct evidence of their improper behavior.

ZH: 这些文字是佐证他们之间的交流。
EN: These written words are evidence of their communication.

ZH: 这件物品是这个城市历史的活生生的佐证。
EN: This item is living proof of the history of this city.

ZH: 这些采访记录为新闻报道提供了佐证。
EN: These interview transcripts provide evidence for the news report.
